<i>Norris is fifth.</i>

330
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:35,160
- Good race.
<i>- Well done.</i>

331
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:38,640
<i>What a grandstand finish.
Unbelievable.</i>

332
00:21:39,320 --> 00:21:40,680
I'm starting to get frustrated

