00:21:40,760 --> 00:21:42,920
because nothing seems to go right
for me at the moment.

334
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:52,960
<i>Carlos Sainz,
heading out onto the grid.</i>

335
00:21:58,760 --> 00:22:00,960
There's some smoke
coming out of the car.

