00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:31,320
...it's the biggest disappointment.

344
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:34,536
- <i>Lando Norris in 11th.</i>
- I feel very down at the moment.

345
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:37,080
<i>This, the scrap
for the final points place.</i>

346
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,160
And upset.

347
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:41,360
I've lost 30 or more points this year.

