00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:22,120
Every professional athlete needs

355
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,360
their own time.

356
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:27,160
My family has always been next to me.

357
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,400
It's where I feel the most comfortable.

358
00:23:30,040 --> 00:23:34,320
Come on.
Let's get going quick no?

