00:23:40,320 --> 00:23:44,960
When he's here,
in a way, he's recharging batteries.

362
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,480
You ready?

363
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:54,400
The life
of the Formula 1 driver is not easy.

364
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:58,120
Motorsport is like that.
Motorsport is up and down.

365
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:02,680
And to have somebody you know
you can trust is, uh, super crucial.

366
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:03,840
Okay.

367
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:10,840
Terrible!

368
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:13,080
When things go wrong,

369
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:14,920
you need to be honest with yourself.

370
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:19,920
Learn from the bad things,
and if you need to cry, you cry,

371
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:23,160
but learn, make the mistakes,

